notes: The Kelligrews Ecological Enhancement Program (KEEP) Water Quality Monitoring has been underway since 2014 in partnership with Northeast Avalon ACAP, who encouraged KEEP to undertake water monitoring and provided monitoring equipment. KEEP has monitoring sites along the Lower Gully River, the Kelligrews River, and the Foxtrap River. notes_translated.en: The Kelligrews Ecological Enhancement Program (KEEP) Water Quality Monitoring has been underway since 2014 in partnership with Northeast Avalon ACAP, who encouraged KEEP to undertake water monitoring and provided monitoring equipment. KEEP has monitoring sites along the Lower Gully River, the Kelligrews River, and the Foxtrap River. Volunteers use a multi-parameter water quality sonde to collect water quality data in-situ to monitor the health of these three waterways.
notes_translated.fr: Le suivi de la qualité de l'eau du Kelligrews Ecological Enhancement Program (KEEP) est en cours depuis 2014 en partenariat avec Northeast Avalon ACAP, qui a encouragé KEEP à effectuer une surveillance de l'eau et a fourni du matériel de surveillance. KEEP possède des sites de surveillance le long du Lower Gully, de la rivière Kelligrews et de la rivière Foxtrap. Les bénévoles utilisent une sonde de qualité de l'eau à paramètres multiples pour recueillir des données sur la qualité de l'eau in situ afin de surveiller l'état de ces trois cours d'eau.
